features: FOIL DESIGN: The gold foil hearts pattern are printed on the paper, bringing the most sincere blessings to your friends and families. Diverse colors and interesting pattern design will make the recipient of the gift happier.

SUITABLE SIZE: 43cm wide x 10m long. Wikadlik gold wrapping paper roll is not a standard width, more narrow than usual size, perfect for medium and small gifts. Add a unique touch to your family, friends or child's party celebration!

High Quality: Wikadlik gift wrapping paper is made of high-quality paper material that feels luxurious to the touch—almost as if it is inviting you to start wrapping. Not folded so no creases, easy to cut.

SHARE HAPPINESS: Wrap every gift with Wikadlik birthday wrapping paper, making each moment an unforgettable memory. Whoever receives such a carefully wrapped gift will feel your love and blessing for the special day, bringing endless laughter and happiness.
MULTI-USE OCCASION: Make birthdays, baby showers, bridal showers, weddings and holidays more special with gifts wrapped. This versatile present packing paper can be used for DIY crafts as well.
